label scene14:
    
    scene bg lernaean_swamps with fade

    'As Hercules navigates the perilous Lernaean Swamps, the air is heavy with anticipation. Each step carries the weight of the unknown.'

    show hercules
    with dissolve

    hercules 'These swamps are treacherous... I must tread carefully.'

    show hercules at left with easeinleft
    show iolaus at right
    with dissolve

    iolaus 'Hercules, my friend! Fear not, it is I, Iolaus, your faithful companion.'

    hercules "Iolaus... forgive my momentary distrust. It's a perilous journey, and caution has become second nature."

    iolaus 'Hercules, Zeus himself came to me in a vision. He warned me of the danger that befalls you in these Lernaean Swamps. Without hesitation, I knew I had to come to your aid.'

    hercules 'Iolaus, my true friend, your presence here brings me great comfort. Together, we shall face whatever challenges await us.'

    'Sounds of the Swamps grow louder and more foreboding, as if the very essence of the swamp conspires against them.'

    jump scene15